@startuml
skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor White
    BorderColor Black
}
skinparam circle {
    BackgroundColor White
    BorderColor Black
}

rectangle "User" as User
circle "1.0\nInput Text" as P1
circle "2.0\nNormalize Data" as P2
circle "3.0\nCalculate Simhash" as P3
circle "4.0\nML Predictor" as P4
circle "5.0\nStore Result" as P5

queue "Reviews Collection (MongoDB)" as DB
rectangle "Alert Module" as Admin

User -> P1 : Submit Review
P1 -> P2 : Raw Text
P2 -> P3 : Normalized String
P3 <--> DB : Check Duplicates
P3 -> P4 : Hash Features
P4 -> P5 : Fake/Real Score
P5 -> DB : Save Report
P5 -> User : Display Verdict
P5 -> Admin : High Risk Alert

@enduml
